9; IV-L-5, 0/4 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[187,201,1341,1367]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">–</emphasis>
6. Leg claw length (all legs) 28 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[552,566,1341,1367]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">–</emphasis>
<date box="[566,679,1341,1367]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="1940-09-18">
40 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[601,615,1341,1367]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">–</emphasis>
